    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine currently struggles to start and will require a major overhaul to be roadworthy again, and the transmission exhibits significant slipping. The body has extensive rust spots, particularly around the wheel wells, and several large dents on the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears and stains, and the electronics are inconsistent. It will likely need to be towed from its current location.",
      "price": 4500.0,
