    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the most exacting standards. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original luster. Mechanically uncompromising and aesthetically pristine, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber.",
